# MD3 Expressive — News UI Starter (Mobile-First + Desktop)

## 0. Platform Assumptions (Locked)

* **Primary:** Mobile-first web (reading, scrolling, quick navigation)
* **Secondary:** Desktop newsroom (wide layouts, multi-column, scanning)
* Interaction model: mouse + keyboard + touch
* Navigation: web header + responsive drawer (not Android bottom nav)

---

## 1. Color Role Mapping — News-Specific (MD3)

### 1.1 Global surfaces

| Area                             | MD3 role               |
| -------------------------------- | ---------------------- |
| App background                   | `background`           |
| Page base surface                | `surface`              |
| Card / section container         | `surfaceContainerLow`  |
| Elevated blocks (hero, breaking) | `surfaceContainerHigh` |
| Divider / subtle borders         | `outlineVariant`       |

Rule:

* News pages live on **surface containers**, not flat white.
* Depth is communicated via **container roles**, not shadows everywhere.

---

### 1.2 Hero / Featured Article

| Element                         | Role                                          |
| ------------------------------- | --------------------------------------------- |
| Hero container                  | `surfaceContainerHigh`                        |
| Headline text                   | `onSurface`                                   |
| Category chip                   | `secondaryContainer` + `onSecondaryContainer` |
| Image overlay scrim (if needed) | `scrim` (low opacity only)                    |

Rules:

* Hero **must be the LCP**.
* No color gradients unless derived from tokens.
* Headline contrast must meet accessibility without text shadows.

---

### 1.3 Section Grids (Politik, Ekonomi, Olahraga, etc.)

| Element              | Role                   |
| -------------------- | ---------------------- |
| Section background   | `surfaceContainer`     |
| Section title        | `onSurface`            |
| Post card background | `surfaceContainerLow`  |
| Hover/focus state    | `surfaceContainerHigh` |

Rules:

* Sections are visually separated by **container roles**, not borders.
* Grid cards never use `primary` background.

---

### 1.4 Article Meta (Byline, Date, Read Time)

| Element     | Role               |
| ----------- | ------------------ |
| Meta text   | `onSurfaceVariant` |
| Author link | `primary`          |
| Icons       | `onSurfaceVariant` |

Rules:

* Meta must visually recede.
* No italics for body readability; hierarchy via size + color only.

---

### 1.5 Chips (Category / Tags)

| Type              | Role                                  |
| ----------------- | ------------------------------------- |
| Default chip      | `secondaryContainer`                  |
| On chip text      | `onSecondaryContainer`                |
| Selected / active | `primaryContainer`                    |
| Disabled          | `surfaceVariant` + `onSurfaceVariant` |

Rules:

* Chips are **informational**, not primary actions.
* Rounded but not pill-exaggerated.

---

### 1.6 Breaking News Banner / Ticker

| Element           | Role               |
| ----------------- | ------------------ |
| Banner background | `errorContainer`   |
| Text              | `onErrorContainer` |
| Divider           | `outline`          |

Rules:

* Used sparingly.
* Static or cached text only (no live polling in HTML).
* No animation that affects LCP or CLS.

