## 5. Component Composition (MD3-ish, Web-Native)

### 5.1 Header / Top App Bar

* Single row
* Left: logo
* Center (desktop): section navigation
* Right: search + menu
* Uses `surfaceContainerLow`

No sticky animations on scroll for first iteration.

---

### 5.2 Post Card

Structure:

```
Card (surfaceContainerLow)
 ├─ Image (optional)
 ├─ Category chip
 ├─ Title
 ├─ Meta (date · read time)
```

Rules:

* Whole card is clickable.
* Focus ring visible on keyboard nav.
* No shadow stack.

---

### 5.3 Article Layout

```
<article>
 ├─ Header
 │   ├─ Category chip
 │   ├─ H1 headline
 │   ├─ Meta (author, date, read time)
 │   └─ Featured image (LCP)
 ├─ Body
 ├─ Related posts
 └─ Footer meta
</article>
```

